{"tid":1417763,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"打機請齊裝 隨時救自己一命","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T23:58:59.000Z","uid":14955,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e42d4751ae19ccf4accd05a4f9dd608cbe9c051f","tid":1417763,"uid":14955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:07:07.000Z","msg":"打機冇裝備 有鬼攻擊即刻死<br />\n就算你平時好打得 啲怪一嘢射落眼<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即死</span></span><br />\n希望大家打機都識保護自己 <br />\n保護好眼同口同身體 <br />\n扣少滴血 攻又好 滅火又好 走又好 都郁得快啲<br />\n特別係班村民 齋企都唔該齊裝<br />\n啲怪一打就乜人都打 啲煙亂咁射<br />\n理得你勇士定村民<br />\n保護好自己 勇士都煩少個 攻都安心啲<br />\n<br />\n講到口臭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>齊裝呀！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">上述指玩online game嘅基本原則</span></span>"},{"pid":"445bfc87dc5f4e90f4f4d5006167322bcc24727f","tid":1417763,"uid":14955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"自己推下<br />\n打機見有村民因為0裝被打敗有感<br />\n大家麻煩保護好自己"},{"pid":"79152a22e93b7a47142335931bdaa1d9366dd88b","tid":1417763,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"但係黃大仙街坊多數空裝屌狗 如果齊裝啲狗就話你示威打埋你"},{"pid":"9d2a3505e619039172c19e68ef7196f9c07a67ec","tid":1417763,"uid":164043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:14:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><br />\n<code>「然遍地腥羶，滿街狼犬！」「吾今日死無餘憾，</code><br />\n<code>國事成不成，自有同志者在。」 - 林覺民 1911</code><br />\n<code>「我哋係前世做錯事 所以今世要搞革命！」</code><br />\n<code>- 無名 2019</code></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光</span>明之子  奮起之<span style=\"color: gold;\">時</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">復</span>赴抗暴   驍勇世<span style=\"color: gold;\">代</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香</span>城安<img src=\"https://